title: He’s Not Satisfied But I Am
itunes:title: He’s Not Satisfied But I Am
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I’m married to my college sweetheart and he’s a great man but we don’t get along now. I wore the pants in our family for years because I made the most money. Back then, all he could do is please me and cater to me. I got used to it and it worked fine for me. He couldn’t wait to get a better paying job and then switch back to wearing the pants in our marriage................................
